 <purpose>
 The Product view definition relationship application module supports the requirement 
 to represent context-dependent relationships between definitions of product versions.
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
 <li>context-dependent relationship between two product definitions;</li>
 <li>representation of the fact that a product version is used in another one;</li>
 </inscope>

